ComicInfo.Summary: Another Me, Another U: Duplicates from the parallel world Earth-A have been messing up continuity in the Marvel Universe for years, but with the help of Reed Richards, Code: Blue; and the law firm of Goodman, Leiber, Kurtzburg, Holliway, and Book, Jennifer Walters resolves the situation and regains her She-Hulk persona.
